addrchain (2.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of addrchain v2
  * Blockchain-based network address management replacing DHCP
  * Linux kernel module (via DKMS) + userspace daemon + CLI
  * IPv4, IPv6, and POOL 256-bit address support
  * VPN tunnel management (WireGuard, IPsec, POOL)
  * Subnet management with CIDR validation
  * Network partitioning with cross-partition deny-by-default
  * Peer autodiscovery (multicast, broadcast, mDNS, static)

 -- Amos Davis <amosdavis@users.noreply.github.com>  Sat, 15 Feb 2026 22:00:00 +0000
